{
  "page": "Jaenara Belaerys",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Jaenara Belaerys</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jaenara_Belaerys_and_Terrax_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jaenara Belaerys and Terrax by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Jaenara_Belaerys_and_Terrax_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/350px-Jaenara_Belaerys_and_Terrax_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"303\" srcset=\"/images/f/fa/Jaenara_Belaerys_and_Terrax_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Jaenara and her dragon <a href=\"/index.php/Terrax\" title=\"Terrax\">Terrax</a>, by coldraindropsss</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Belaerys_family\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Belaerys family\">Belaerys family</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valyrians\" title=\"Valyrians\">Valyrian</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jaenara Belaerys</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonrider\" title=\"Dragonrider\">dragonrider</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jaenara_Belaerys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jaenara flew her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Terrax\" title=\"Terrax\">Terrax</a>, farther south in <a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a> than anyone had gone before. She returned to the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a> after three years, having found only endless jungle, deserts, and mountains. Jaenara declared that Sothoryos was as large as <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and \"a land without end\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jaenara_Belaerys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: Sothoryos.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limi